      <h1 class="learntoplay_text_h">Using Armor</h1>

      Protect yourself as you surf the web! Armor is an appropriate way to protect yourself from the ravages of Mines.  Each piece of armor can protect you from three mines before it breaks.<br /><br />

      <% if current_user.is_armored? %>
