        You are protected. You can keep an eye on your Armor in the toolbar, and make sure your&nbsp; <img src="/images/learn/armor/armor.png" alt="Armor" />&nbsp; is on!<br /><br />
        
        <h4>Now, click below to learn about portals.</h4>

  		  <a href="/learn/portals" class="learntoplay_portals_next" style="margin-top:5px;">&nbsp;</a>
        
      <% else %>
        
        <h3 class="learntoplay_text_h">Give It a Try</h3>
      
